  "text": "RNASeq analysis was performed using the DESeq R package [CITATION_1] . Reads were normalized according to the library complexity. Gene annotation was obtained from ENSEMBL (BDGP6 version) using the biomaRt R package (Smedley et al., 2009) . Genes were flagged as significantly changing expression if the corresponding adjusted p-values were below 0.05. ",
